<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<h1>Weathers</h1>
<script>
  function goAnotherPage(value){
    window.location =value
  }
</script>
您選擇的地區為<%= @site %>，請選擇您要的地區：
<select onchange ="goAnotherPage(this.value)">
  <option value="">請選擇</option>
  <% @select.each do |option| %>
    <option value="<%= weathers_weatherList_path(option) %>"><%= option =%></option>
  <% end %>
</select>

<% if @weathers.length>0 %>
  <%= line_chart  @data, @options%>

  <table class="table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>地區</th>
        <th>風向</th>
        <th>風級</th>
        <th>溫度</th>
        <th>天氣</th>
        <th>更新日期</th>
        <th colspan="3"></th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
  
    <tbody>
      <% @weathers.each do |weather| %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= weather.siteName %></td>
            <td><%= weather.windDirection %></td>
            <td><%= weather.windPower %></td>
            <td><%= weather.temperature %></td>
            <td><%= weather.weather %></td>
            <td><%= weather.dataCreationDate %></td>
          </tr>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
<% else %>
  <br>
  抱歉，查無此地區，請重新選擇!
<% end %>
<br>
